detailview : https://codepen.io/towfique-elahe/pen/qBooPxo


eventRegister template : https://codepen.io/Aakash-dev/details/NYwPjo

Dekho ye registration form template hai ko use kr k react mai is do rout mai userRegisteration, eventRegisteration component bana k benjna.

http://localhost:3000/registerUser      -> for registering the user
http://localhost:3000/registerEvent     -> for registering the event.

user registereration mai ye saare fields rahenge

firstName : string,
lastName : string
address : {
    street : String,
    city : String,
    state : String,
    zipCode : String,
},
phone : String,
    length : 10
    required : true
},
email : {
    type : String,
    require :true
},
password : {
        type :String,
        minLength : 8,
        maxLength :15,
        require :true
},


 type : {
        type : String,
        required : true
    },    //['workshops', 'online streaming event', 'comedy show', 'sprituality', 'Music show', 'Talks', 'other'] //dropdownbox
    language : {
        type : String,
        required : true
    }, //['hindi', 'english', 'telu', 'punjabi', 'bengali', 'others'],  //dropdownbox
    money : {
        type : Number,
        required : true
    }, 
    city : String,
    state : String,
    zipcode : String,
    title : {
        type : String,
        required : true
    },
    detail : {
        type : String,
        required : true
    },
    startTime : {
        type : Date,
        required : true
    },
    endTime : Date,
    imgUrl :{
        required :true,
        type : String
    }